The paper discusses machine learning-based techniques for anomaly detection in intrusion detection systems. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses various machine learning algorithms and techniques, which are commonly used in other sub-categories of computer science such as machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and software engineering (cs.SE).
